# Playground Architecture

## What It Does

The Design Playground is an AI-powered visual component iteration tool. Users discover components, drag them onto an infinite canvas, generate AI-powered layout/style variations, compare side-by-side, and copy code back.

## System Flow

```
Sidebar (components)  →  Canvas (React Flow)  →  Iterate Dialog
                                                       ↓
                                              Provider (Cursor/Claude CLI)
                                                       ↓
                                              API (/generate) spawns agent
                                                       ↓
                                              Agent writes iteration .tsx files
                                                       ↓
                                              File watcher detects tree.json change
                                                       ↓
                                              SSE event → IterationNode renders on canvas
```

## Folder Map

| Folder | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `PlaygroundClient.tsx` | Main orchestrator — discovery, HMR recovery |
| `PlaygroundCanvas.tsx` | React Flow canvas with nodes/edges |
| `PlaygroundSidebar.tsx` | Component browser & drag source |
| `PlaygroundHeader.tsx` | Top toolbar, model settings |
| `registry.tsx` | Component registry (all draggable components) — see @registry.mdc |
| `nodes/` | Canvas node components — see @canvas/nodes.mdc |
| `hooks/` | React hooks — see @canvas/hooks.mdc |
| `iterations/` | Generated iteration files — see @iterations/guide.mdc |
| `prompts/` | AI prompt templates — see @generation/prompts.mdc |
| `lib/providers/` | AI provider integrations — see @generation/providers.mdc |
| `lib/constants.ts` | Event names, layout defaults, feature flags (25KB) |
| `api/` | Backend route handlers — see @generation/api-routes.mdc |
| `skills/` | AI creative direction — see @ui/skills.mdc |
| `data/` | Mock data files for components |
| `previews/` | Playground-specific component wrappers |
| `ui/` | Local shadcn/ui components — see @ui/components.mdc |
| `docs/` | This documentation |

## Key Entities

- **Registry Items**: Components registered in `registry.tsx` with ID, lazy import, mock props, optional size
- **Canvas Nodes**: ComponentNode (original), IterationNode (variation), SkeletonNode (loading), ImageNode
- **Iterations**: AI-generated `.tsx` variation files in `iterations/`, tracked in `tree.json`
- **Providers**: Cursor CLI or Claude Code CLI — abstractions for spawning AI agents

## State

- **Canvas**: localStorage (persisted across sessions)
- **Model Settings**: zustand + localStorage (`model-settings-store.ts`)
- **Discovery**: disk (`discovery.json`)
- **Iterations**: disk (`.tsx` files + `tree.json` + `index.ts`)

See @conventions/state.mdc for details.
